title: Memoirs of the Torrey Botanical Club

contents.note: JSTOR (full text also available; after 1924 may require subscription or payment)

additional-notes: Some issues may have distinct titles.  Before concluding an issue with such a title is in the public domain, check for book renewals of that title.  We have not systematically surveyed those titles, but only searched for renewal records specifically mentioning the Torrey Botanical Club.
Spot-checks of issues prior to 1989 did not turn up copyright notices.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Paul Ryersbach for copyright research on this title.
